entially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.','Test 8','','inherit','closed','closed','','323-revision-v1','','','2017-07-01 09:05:16','2017-07-01 09:05:16','',323,'http://localhost/axovel_new/323-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(325,1,'2017-07-15 09:05:39','2017-07-15 09:05:39','This blog will explain to read image data from CSV file and remove the existing product image then assign new product image in magento2 programmatically. \r\n\r\nCheck the CSV format in the screen shot Column A represent product SKU and column B your image name. The images are located on your local file system.\r\n<div class=\"blog_container\">\r\n<img src=\"http://axovel.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/csv-screen-shot2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"287\" height=\"214\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-392\" />\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"blog_container\">\r\n<pre>\r\nuse Magento\\Framework\\App\\Bootstrap;\r\ninclude(\'app/bootstrap.php\');\r\n$bootstrap = Bootstrap::create(BP, $_SERVER);\r\n\r\n$objectManager = $bootstrap->getObjectManager();\r\n\r\n$state = $objectManager->get(\'Magento\\Framework\\App\\State\');\r\n$state->setAreaCode(\'frontend\');\r\n\r\n$_product = $objectManager->create(\'Magento\\Catalog\\Api\\ProductRepositoryInterface\');\r\n$csvProcessor = $objectManager->create(\'\\Magento\\Framework\\File\\Csv\');\r\n$filesystem = $objectManager->create(\'Magento\\Framework\\Filesystem\');\r\n/** @var \\Magento\\Framework\\Filesystem\\Directory\\WriteInterface $mediaDirectory */\r\n\r\n$mediaDirectory = $filesystem->getDirectoryWrite(\\Magento\\Framework\\App\\Filesystem\\DirectoryList::MEDIA);\r\n\r\n$mediaPath = $mediaDirectory->getAbsolutePath();\r\n$path = getcwd();\r\n$importProductRawData = $csvProcessor->getData($path.\'/custom.csv\');// replace csv name with your csv name \r\n \r\n \r\n foreach ($importProductRawData as $rowIndex => $dataRow) {\r\n  try{\r\n     	$pro = $_product->get($dataRow[0]); // code to get product data by sku\r\n     	\r\n	$existingMediaGalleryEntries = $pro->getMediaGalleryEntries(); // code to get existing image details\r\n	\r\n       foreach ($existingMediaGalleryEntries as $key => $entry) {\r\n	  unset($existingMediaGalleryEntries[$key]); // removing exisiting image\r\n	}\r\n	 $pro->setMediaGalleryEntries($existingMediaGalleryEntries);\r\n	 $_product->save($pro);\r\n\r\n	 /*Add Images To The Product*/\r\n	  $pro = $_product->get($dataRow[0]);\r\n	  $imagePath = $mediaPath .\'import/\'.$dataRow[1]; // path of the image\r\n	  $pro->addImageToMediaGallery($imagePath, array(\'image\', \'small_image\', \'thumbnail\'), false, false);  \r\n	 $pro->save();      \r\n	     		\r\n	    \r\n 	}\r\n 	catch(\\Exception $e){\r\n 		echo \'Image Not Updated = \'.$dataRow[0]; echo \'<br>\';	\r\n 	}\r\n   \r\n }\r\necho \'Product Images Uploaded Successfully\';\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nShare you feedback its important to us.','Add product image  programmtically in magento 2','','publish','open','open','','add-product-image-magento2','','','2017-10-23 11:00:34','2017-10-23 11:00:34','',0,'http://localhost/axovel_new/?p=325',0,'post','',2),(326,1,'2017-07-01 09:05:39','2017-07-01 09:05:39','Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.','Test 10','','inherit','closed','closed','','325-revision-v1','','','2017-07-01 09:05:39','2017-07-01 09:05:39','',325,'http://localhost/axovel_new/325-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(327,1,'2017-07-01 09:06:10','2017-07-01 09:06:10','This blog will explain to read data from CSV file and assign product attribute in magento2 programmatically. Check the CSV format in the screen shot Column A represent product SKU and column B to E are contained option setup for product attributes.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"blog_container\">\r\n<img src=\"http://axovel.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/csv-screen-shot1-1-300x130.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"130\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-387\" />\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"blog_container\">\r\n<pre>\r\nuse Magento\\Framework\\App\\Bootstrap;\r\ninclude(\'app/bootstrap.php\');\r\n$bootstrap = Bootstrap::create(BP, $_SERVER);\r\n\r\n$objectManager = $bootstrap->getObjectManager();\r\n\r\n$state = $objectManager->get(\'Magento\\Framework\\App\\State\');\r\n$state->setAreaCode(\'frontend\');\r\n\r\n\r\n$_product = $objectManager->create(\'Magento\\Catalog\\Api\\ProductRepositoryInterface\');\r\n$csvProcessor = $objectManager->create(\'\\Magento\\Framework\\File\\Csv\');\r\n\r\n$path = getcwd();\r\n$importProductRawData = $csvProcessor->getData($path.\'/custom.csv\'); \r\n\r\n                      //replace custom.csv with your csv file name.\r\n \r\n// function is used to fetch the attribute option id\r\nfunction attributeCode($attribute,$label,$pro){\r\n return $pro->getResource()->getAttribute($attribute)->getSource()->getOptionId($label);\r\n}  \r\n\r\n// end of function\r\n\r\n foreach ($importProductRawData as $rowIndex => $dataRow) {\r\n  \r\n 	try{\r\n     	$pro = $_product->get($dataRow[0]);\r\n     	      	 	\r\n     	  	$units    = attributeCode(\'units\',$dataRow[1],$pro);\r\n     	  	$size     = attributeCode(\'size\',$dataRow[2],$pro);\r\n     	  	$material = attributeCode(\'material\',$dataRow[3],$pro);\r\n     	  	$color    = attributeCode(\'color\',$dataRow[4],$pro);\r\n     	  	     	  	     	 	\r\n	     	 $pro->setStoreId(0)\r\n	     	 	->setDescription($dataRow[3])\r\n	     	 	->setUnits($units)\r\n	      	        ->setSize($size)\r\n	     	 	->setMaterial($material)\r\n	     	 	->setColor($color)\r\n	     	 	->save();\r\n     	 	   \r\n	}\r\n 	catch(\\Exception $e){\r\n 		echo \'Attribute Not Updated = \'.$dataRow[0]; echo \'<br>\';\r\n 		\r\n 	}\r\n   \r\n }\r\necho \'Attribute Updated Successfully\';\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nHope this blog help you and we continue to share our knowledge on Axovel blog','How to assign products attribute in Magento2 Programmatically','','publish','open','open','','adding-product-attribute-magento2','','','2017-07-27 12:36:09','2017-07-27 12:36:09','',0,'http://localhost/axovel_new/?p=327',0,'post','',0),(328,1,'2017-07-01 09:06:10','2017-07-01 09:06:10','Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.','Test','','inherit','closed','closed','','327-revision-v1','','','2017-07-01 09:06:10','2017-07-01 09:06:10','',327,'http://localhost/axovel_new/327-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(331,1,'2017-07-26 09:10:57','2017-07-26 09:10:57','This blog will explain to read data from csv file and assign related product in magento2 programmatically. Check the csv format in screen shot Column A represent parent product sku and column B to E are contain sku of related product.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"blog_container\">\r\n<a href=\"http://axovel.com/test-5-2/csv-screen-shot-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-365\"><img src=\"http://axovel.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/csv-screen-shot.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"788\" height=\"264\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-365\" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"blog_container\">\r\n<pre>\r\n\r\nuse Magento\\Framework\\App\\Bootstrap;\r\ninclude(\'app/bootstrap.php\');\r\n$bootstrap = Bootstrap::create(BP, $_SERVER);\r\n\r\n$objectManager = $bootstrap->getObjectManager();\r\n\r\n$state = $objectManager->get(\'Magento\\Framework\\App\\State\');\r\n$state->setAreaCode(\'frontend\');\r\n\r\n$_product = $objectManager->create(\'Magento\\Catalog\\Api\\ProductRepositoryInterface\');\r\n$csvProcessor = $objectManager->create(\'\\Magento\\Framework\\File\\Csv\');\r\n\r\n$path = getcwd();\r\n$importProductRawData = $csvProcessor->getData($path.\'/related_product_thirstybox.csv\');\r\n \r\nforeach ($importProductRawData as $rowIndex => $dataRow) \r\n{\r\n\r\ntry{\r\n     $pro = $_product->get($dataRow[0]);   //getting of parent product sku\r\n      if($pro){\r\n\r\n       for($i=1;$i<=4;$i++){\r\n        if($dataRow[$i]){\r\n             $linkedProduct = $_product->get($dataRow[$i]);\r\n         if($linkedProduct) \r\n         {\r\n	 $productLink = $objectManager->create(\'Magento\\Catalog\\Api\\Data\\ProductLinkInterface\')\r\n	               ->setSku($dataRow[0])                // Parent productsku\r\n	               ->setLinkedProductSku($dataRow[$i]) // Related product sku\r\n	                ->setPosition($i)                 //  position of related product          \r\n		        ->setLinkType(\"related\");\r\n\r\n	   $linkData[] = $productLink;\r\n  	 }\r\n       }\r\n     }\r\n\r\n        $pro->setProductLinks($linkData)->save();  //Saving realted product data\r\n\r\n    }\r\n       echo \"Updated Successfully\"; echo $dataRow[0]; \r\n   }\r\n 	catch(Exception $e){\r\n 		echo \'Not Updated = \'.$dataRow[0]; echo \'<br>\';\r\n 	}\r\n}\r\necho \'Product assigned Successfully\';\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>','How to add related products in Magento2 Programmatically','','publish','open','open','','blog-related-product','','','2017-08-14 11:25:20','2017-08-14 11:25:20','',0,'http://localhost/axovel_new/?p=331',0,'post','',2),(332,1,'2017-07-01 09:10:57','2017-07-01 09:10:57','asdasd','Test 5','','inherit','closed','closed','','331-revision-v1','','','2017-07-01 09:10:57','2017-07-01 09:10:57','',331,'http://localhost/axovel_new/331-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(333,1,'2017-07-01 09:22:29','2017-07-01 09:22:29','Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the ','Test 5','','inherit','closed','closed','','331-revision-v1','','','2017-07-01 09:22:29','2017-07-01 09:22:29','',331,'http://localhost/axovel_new/331-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(334,1,'2017-07-01 09:23:09','2017-07-01 09:23:09','Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.','Test 5','','inherit','closed','closed','','331-revision-v1','','','2017-07-01 09:23:09','2017-07-01 09:23:09','',331,'http://localhost/axovel_new/331-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(335,1,'2017-07-01 10:25:30','2017-07-01 10:25:30',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','335','','','2017-07-01 10:25:30','2017-07-01 10:25:30','',0,'http://192.241.153.62/axovel/?p=335',6,'nav_menu_item','',0),(336,1,'2017-07-01 10:28:12','2017-07-01 10:28:12','<!-- Page Content -->\r\n    <section class=\"wrapper_section\">\r\n        <section class=\"banner_