http://axovel.com/321-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(409,1,'2017-07-28 12:21:57','2017-07-28 12:21:57','Below are code snippets which will help you convert the Density-independent Pixels (dp) to Pixels and vice versa.\n\nConvert scale-independent pixel(sp) to Pixels (px) and vice versa.\n\n<strong>Code to convert Dp to pixels</strong>\n<pre>public static int dpToPx(Context context, int dp) \n{\n    DisplayMetrics displayMetrics = context.getResources().getDisplayMetrics();\n    int px = Math.round(dp * (displayMetrics.xdpi / DisplayMetrics.DENSITY_DEFAULT));\n    return px;\n}\n\n</pre>\n<strong>Code to convert pixels to Dp</strong>\n<pre>public static int pxToDp(Context context, int px) \n{\n    DisplayMetrics displayMetrics = context.getResources().getDisplayMetrics();\n    int dp = Math.round(px / (displayMetrics.xdpi / DisplayMetrics.DENSITY_DEFAULT));\n    return dp;\n}\n</pre>\n<strong>Code to convert pixels to Sp </strong>\n<pre>public static float pixelsToSp(Context context, float px) \n{\n    float scaledDensity = context.getResources().getDisplayMetrics().scaledDensity;\n    return px / scaledDensity;\n}\n\n</pre>\n<strong>Code to convert Sp to pixels</strong>\n<pre>public static int spToPixel(Context context, int sp) {\n    float scaledDensity = context.getResources().getDisplayMetrics().scaledDensity;\n    return (int) (sp * scaledDensity);\n}\n</pre>','Density converter methods (dp to pixels,  pixels to dp,  sp to pixels,  pixels to sp) Android','','inherit','closed','closed','','313-autosave-v1','','','2017-07-28 12:21:57','2017-07-28 12:21:57','',313,'http://axovel.com/313-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(410,1,'2017-07-28 13:16:05','2017-07-28 13:16:05','In thisblog we are displaying the code\n<pre>\nUse the following code to open gallery-\nIntent intent = new Intent(Intent.ACTION_GET_CONTENT);\nintent.setType(\"image/*\");\nstartActivityForResult(intent, GALLERY_REQUEST_CODE);\n\nGet image in onActivityResult() of Activity-\n@Override\nprotected void onActivityResult(int requestCode, int resultCode, Intent data) {\n    super.onActivityResult(requestCode, resultCode, data);\n\n    if (resultCode == RESULT_OK) {\n        if (requestCode == GALLERY_REQUEST_CODE) {\n           \n            try {\n                InputStream inputStream = getContentResolver().openInputStream(data.getData());\n\n                BitmapFactory.Options options = new BitmapFactory.Options();\n                options.inJustDecodeBounds = true;\n                BitmapFactory.decodeStream(inputStream, null, options);\n\n                Log.d(\"Actual size\", \"\" + options.outWidth + \"   \" + options.outHeight);\n\n                if ((options.outWidth == -1) || (options.outHeight == -1)) {\n                    Toast.makeText(RegisterBusinessActivity.this, Unable to get image, Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();\n                    return;\n                }\n\n		  // Define your required image size here..\n                int requiredSize = Utills.dpToPx(getApplicationContext(), 100);\n                if (options.outWidth &gt; requiredSize || options.outHeight &gt; requiredSize) {\n                    options.inSampleSize = (options.outHeight &gt; options.outWidth) ? (options.outHeight / requiredSize) : (options.outWidth / requiredSize);\n                }\n\n                options.inJustDecodeBounds = false;\n                inputStream = getContentResolver().openInputStream(data.getData());\n\n		 // This is scaled bitmap..\n                Bitmap selectedThumbBitmap = BitmapFactory.decodeStream(inputStream, null, options);\n\n                Log.d(\"After scaling\", \"\" + selectedThumbBitmap.getWidth() + \"   \" + selectedThumbBitmap.getHeight());\n\n            } catch (FileNotFoundException e) {\n                Toast.makeText(RegisterBusinessActivity.this, Unable to get image,, Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();\n                e.printStackTrace();\n            }\n\n        }\n    }\n}\n</pre>','Get scaled bitmap from gallery in App  Andr